      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Up for sale is a reliable vehicle in good overall condition, ideal for someone seeking a dependable daily driver. The engine runs strong and the transmission shifts smoothly, reflecting a consistent maintenance schedule. While the exterior and interior show some minor signs of normal wear and tear consistent with its age, the car remains clean, well-cared for, and ready for the road without any immediate repair needs.",
