    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for those needing a functional daily driver on a budget. The engine starts up without issue and the car is fully drivable, though prospective buyers should note some minor hesitation in the transmission during gear shifts. The exterior and interior show signs of typical wear and tear consistent with its age, but all essential safety features are intact. It is a solid candidate for someone willing to perform some light maintenance to bring it back to its best.",
