      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present an exemplary specimen of automotive engineering, maintained to the highest standards of preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, featuring a flawless exterior and an interior that exhibits no signs of wear. Every mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure it meets our exacting performance criteria. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a motorcar of uncompromising quality and provenance.",
